No. 77,

Misc.

Greene v. United States. James H. Heller for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Warren Olney, III, then Assistant Attorney General, Roger Fisher and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit granted.
